osad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f6224e8ed0380418aea77129d0f51a765cd4cf","tid":245244,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T21:53:03.000Z","msg":"而家真係冇乜人用正宗手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd5bf7f98e446cbf254354d7f3b0c912e579a99","tid":245244,"uid":46631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T22:22:49.000Z","msg":"用到黎食飯,夾餸,夾麵咪得"},{"pid":"21b5da95ee3bad616c22df5f5d50fd75103103c0","tid":245244,"uid":44814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T01:55:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家真係冇乜人用正宗手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 <br />\n我一開始都唔係正宗手勢 但後尾覺得呢個係spirit黎要學返 無理由自己傳統都唔學好 宜家發現正宗手勢先易夾野"},{"pid":"de2b160005cc10a647e5c90ab8f166b0309a9859","tid":245244,"uid":35504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>而家真係冇乜人用正宗手勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係囉 <br />\n我一開始都唔係正宗手勢 但後尾覺得呢個係spirit黎要學返 無理由自己傳統都唔學好 宜家發現正宗手勢先易夾野</blockquote><br />\n真係易夾好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176db5aca1ca7bef1d5c6566dddcb2b19e5cb47c","tid":245244,"uid":48064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"細個老母話夾到野就得<br />\n所以到而家都唔識渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}